Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.89,0:22:11.18,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,BERSAMBUNG
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.59,0:01:35.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.76,0:01:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu mencium wangi bunga\Ntiap kali melewati toko ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.83,0:01:42.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran sekali ingin masuk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.61,0:01:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.94,0:01:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shizuka, beri tahu aku\Njika ada bunga yang kau suka.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.82,0:01:49.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Aku boleh memilih bunga yang kusuka?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.68,0:01:51.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tentu saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.00,0:01:53.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bunga apa yang kau inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.67,0:01:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kalau begitu... mawar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:01:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kebetulan, mawar adalah\Nrekomendasiku hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.04,0:02:05.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, kami mau beli tiga.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.52,0:02:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.03,0:02:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayang, tolong bungkuskan bunganya!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.55,0:02:12.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja, Sayang.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.13,0:02:14.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Mereka akan membawa ini.\N- Dia besar sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.70,0:02:15.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.40,0:02:17.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu suara dari atas?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.49,0:02:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kalian suami istri?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.06,0:02:24.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya. Aku manusia, dan suamiku seorang ogre.\NKami menjalani pernikahan antarras.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.14,0:02:26.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pernikahan antarras...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.22,0:02:29.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami adalah pasangan antarras...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.91,0:02:35.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, kau sering berhenti\Ndi depan toko saat lewat, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.30,0:02:35.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.83,0:02:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maafkan aku.\NItu pasti sangat mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.84,0:02:41.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kami tidak keberatan, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:42.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak sudah mampir hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.91,0:02:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih sudah menunggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.53,0:02:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini bonus bunga Baby's Breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.62,0:02:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih banyak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.01,0:02:52.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia bisa membungkus bunga dengan tangan\Nsebesar itu. Luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di bagian kantor mana\Nsebaiknya kita meletakkan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.73,0:02:57.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seru sekali membayangkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.87,0:03:00.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas kunjungannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.26,0:03:04.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.42,0:03:06.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin di meja lebih bagus?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.55,0:03:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kan bagian tengah ruangan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.67,0:03:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.26,0:03:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suasana kantor akan langsung berubah\Nmenjadi menenangkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:18.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, apa kau suka bunga mawar, Shizuka?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.29,0:03:26.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi sangat menyukainya sejak kau\Nmemberiku mawar sebagai hadiah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.42,0:03:28.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.13,0:03:32.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terkadang, kau mengatakan hal seperti itu\Ntanpa ragu, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.34,0:03:33.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.16,0:03:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, ayo letakkan di atas meja.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.92,0:03:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.01,0:03:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.99,0:03:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:51.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Apa itu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.84,0:03:52.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.94,0:03:53.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi aku menendang pohon.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:03:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.70,0:03:59.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku tidak apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.03,0:04:02.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menendang pohon tidak mungkin\Nmenimbulkan suara sekeras itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.46,0:04:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.85,0:04:05.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak bisa melihat tandukku?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.46,0:04:08.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm? Apa kau termasuk ras bertanduk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.37,0:04:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.10,0:04:12.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begini... aku tidak bisa melihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.32,0:04:13.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.04,0:04:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku mengerti. Jadi, karena itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.67,0:04:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membantumu berdiri.\NUlurkan tanganmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.85,0:04:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.05,0:04:26.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah, kau kuat sekali.\NTerima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.45,0:04:29.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku blasteran ogre dan manusia.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.19,0:04:31.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ogre itu sangat kuat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.18,0:04:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih belum mahir\Nmengendalikan kekuatanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.64,0:04:38.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh ya, tapi kenapa kau menendang pohon itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.04,0:04:40.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku merasa agak kesal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.51,0:04:42.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi aku sedang bermain\Ndengan teman-temanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.30,0:04:46.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kena!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.72,0:04:48.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menyentuhnya dengan lembut,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:04:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku masih tidak bisa\Nmengendalikan kekuatanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:03.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan merepotkan jika mereka menangis\Nsaat aku bermain lagi, jadi aku pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.93,0:05:08.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau seperti penyendiri. Keren sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.45,0:05:10.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan seperti itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.76,0:05:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.91,0:05:17.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menghindar dari masalah tidak akan\Nmembuat segalanya jadi lebih baik.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.10,0:05:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.01,0:05:23.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harus bagaimana, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.05,0:05:28.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yu! Kau pergi ke mana?\NKami mencarimu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.67,0:05:32.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu karena mereka mulai menangis\Ndan tidak mau bermain lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.44,0:05:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi ini kan salah Yu!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.18,0:05:36.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakimu terluka, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.70,0:05:38.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}He-Hei...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.42,0:05:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa kita gunakan ini saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lidi air?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.20,0:05:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika menyentuh dengan ini,\Ntidak akan ada yang terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.81,0:05:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Seperti ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.01,0:05:50.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.88,0:05:53.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, itu bisa digunakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.06,0:05:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, aku punya cakar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.52,0:05:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo gunakan itu dan bermain lagi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.74,0:06:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi agak sulit untuk tahu\Napakah sudah tersentuh atau belum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.30,0:06:03.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, kau benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.54,0:06:04.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, bagaimana jika\Nmenggunakan yang banyak?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.99,0:06:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku punya karet gelang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.60,0:06:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pulang!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.86,0:06:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang kembali!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.92,0:06:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.18,0:06:17.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kami tidak bisa\Nmendapatkan petunjuk apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:19.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.83,0:06:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.59,0:06:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukankah ini pria itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.23,0:06:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Klien kami curiga dia mengedarkan produk\Nperusahaannya di pasar gelap.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.70,0:06:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat ini dia masih berstatus tersangka.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.83,0:06:34.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, apa kutukanku membantu tempo hari?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.18,0:06:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, pada akhirnya dia tidak melakukan\Nhal mencurigakan apa pun hari itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.34,0:06:38.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi tidak ada gunanya?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.09,0:06:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Permisi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.35,0:06:45.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat datang. Apa itu kau, Yu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.59,0:06:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya! Halo, Kak Yako!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.86,0:06:49.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halo.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.03,0:06:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada perlu apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.35,0:06:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Proyek wawancara karier.\NSepertinya ini tugas sekolah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.71,0:06:55.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau mengenal anak itu?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.16,0:06:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia anak penjual bunga yang kami kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.27,0:07:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tonome, ini Yu yang datang\Nuntuk wawancara karier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.11,0:07:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mohon bantuannya untuk wawancara ini!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terima kasih atas minatmu.\NAku Tonome, detektif di agensi ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.33,0:07:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.35,0:07:12.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa ada masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.63,0:07:13.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.80,0:07:16.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah melihat orang ini sebelumnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.23,0:07:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.59,0:07:19.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya. Saat aku sedang bermain\Nbersama teman-temanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:22.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dia sangat marah dan memarahi kami\Nagar tidak bermain di sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.35,0:07:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, apa tempat itu\Nberbahaya untuk bermain?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau ingat di mana lokasinya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.63,0:07:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Iya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.98,0:07:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya. Di sekitar sini?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.92,0:07:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sepertinya begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.15,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan pergi mencari bukti.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.44,0:07:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasus ini bisa ditutup\Njika kita berhasil menangkap basah aksinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.78,0:07:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bukankah itu berbahaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.20,0:07:40.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menyiapkan bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.47,0:07:42.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.07,0:07:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku berangkat sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.32,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, berhati-hatilah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, apa dia akan pergi\Nke tempat yang kuberitahukan tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.21,0:07:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.73,0:07:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.96,0:08:00.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kak Yako, terima kasih\Nsudah mengatur wawancaranya!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:04.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau yakin?\NJarashi akan segera kembali, lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, tidak apa-apa!\NAku pulang dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.39,0:08:08.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sampai jumpa!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.01,0:08:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sedang membuntuti seorang detektif!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.65,0:08:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatan untuk melihatnya\Nberaksi secara langsung!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.65,0:08:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini akan jadi laporan yang bagus!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.19,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, benar.\NAku juga harus mengambil foto.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:33.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.12,0:08:34.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sudah tidak ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.15,0:08:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku hanya memalingkan wajah\Nsebentar saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.79,0:08:39.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana bisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.54,0:08:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Yu? Aku merasa ada yang mengikutiku,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.11,0:08:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi kukira bukan dia.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.07,0:08:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hampir saja. Aku akan pergi\Nke arah lain untuk mengubah jalur.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.15,0:08:58.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nah...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.96,0:09:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada di sekitar sana.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.18,0:09:06.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu, di mana yang lainnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.81,0:09:08.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akan ketahuan jika sekaligus banyak.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.82,0:09:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan membaginya jadi beberapa bagian.\NMana uangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.68,0:09:12.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.39,0:09:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa orang yang satu lagi\Ndari organisasi penerima?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.98,0:09:18.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini kesempatanku untuk\Nmenangkap basah aksi mereka.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei! Sedang apa kau di sana?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.23,0:09:21.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.16,0:09:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyelinap seperti tikus saja!\NSini kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:26.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.83,0:09:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanya sedang mencari seseorang!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.59,0:09:29.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak melakukan apa-apa!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.85,0:09:33.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Bocah ini memotret kita!\N- Yu?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.46,0:09:35.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia juga terus berkeliaran di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:37.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang, aku tidak melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.07,0:09:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, foto bisa jadi masalah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.79,0:09:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh! Benar juga! Anak ini juga\Nberkeliaran di sini kemarin!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.05,0:09:47.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Nak, apa ada seseorang\Nyang menyuruhmu melakukan ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:49.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, tidak ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.15,0:09:53.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, bocah ini kecil, tapi kuat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.08,0:09:55.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia seorang ogre. Tetap waspada.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.68,0:09:59.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial, benar juga! Kalau aku melawan,\Naku bisa melukai mereka!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.22,0:10:02.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.86,0:10:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia berhenti melawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ambil ponselnya dan kurung dia\Ndi ruang belakang.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.07,0:10:08.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, jalan!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.09,0:10:14.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, aku sudah menghapus foto di ponselnya.\NBagaimana sekarang?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.85,0:10:16.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk saat ini, hubungi bos dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.91,0:10:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa yang bertanggung jawab?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.94,0:10:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka akan segera tiba di sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.84,0:10:23.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana ini?\NApa yang akan terjadi padaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.55,0:10:27.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo kita jual dia dengan harga mahal!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.84,0:10:30.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan, dia itu sumber masalah!\NAyo kita tenggelamkan saja!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.01,0:10:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Diam! Berhenti menangis!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:37.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.39,0:10:41.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.38,0:10:42.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.07,0:10:48.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak perlu takut.\NAku sudah memanggil bantuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.69,0:10:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan menampakkan diri sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.36,0:10:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.13,0:10:56.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.23,0:11:00.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shh.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.00,0:11:03.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.74,0:11:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ke-Keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.69,0:11:09.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak bisa melihatnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.13,0:11:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menjadi detektif\Nsaat besar nanti!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.62,0:11:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, gawat sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.53,0:11:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar, 'kan?\NKita perlu mencari cara.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.11,0:11:18.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.94,0:11:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, halo?\NBegini, ada masalah kecil...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.46,0:11:28.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan melepaskan ikatanmu sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.54,0:11:29.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.60,0:11:33.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggalkan bocah itu dan cari tempat lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:34.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.33,0:11:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang benar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:36.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei! Cepat sedikit!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.96,0:11:37.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:40.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Astaga, sungguh merepotkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.59,0:11:41.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:43.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gelap sekali...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.61,0:11:51.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana sekarang?\NAku tidak bisa melihat apa pun.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.30,0:11:53.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tu-tunggu sebentar.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.57,0:11:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.16,0:12:00.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku senang detektif ini ada di sini.\NDia seperti pahlawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Tonome, kenapa Anda\Nmemutuskan untuk menjadi detektif?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.43,0:12:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:10.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu, biar kupikirkan. Dahulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.05,0:12:12.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku ingin seseorang menemukan sesuatu,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.27,0:12:16.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi tidak ada yang bisa menemukannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.01,0:12:18.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hal itu membuatku sangat sedih.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.93,0:12:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, untuk membantu orang lain\Nmenemukan yang mereka cari,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.84,0:12:25.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku pun menjadi detektif.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.44,0:12:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu, ya. Jadi itu sebabnya\NAnda bisa menemukanku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.57,0:12:32.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah, izinkan aku menjawab telepon dulu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.14,0:12:33.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira, apa semuanya baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.32,0:12:40.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah menyusup ke lokasi.\NSaat ini aku sedang bersama Yu.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.13,0:12:42.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yu?! Apa dia baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.10,0:12:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sepertinya dia tidak terluka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.04,0:12:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, syukurlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.54,0:12:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.66,0:12:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.95,0:12:53.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau keberatan jika kita\Nterus berbicara seperti ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.78,0:12:55.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku butuh pengalih perhatian.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:12:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.17,0:13:01.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dahulu kala, di negeri yang jauh...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.15,0:13:02.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa dongeng?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.34,0:13:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau memintanya tiba-tiba, sih!\NApa yang harus kubicarakan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.22,0:13:09.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku! Dongeng juga boleh.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.05,0:13:11.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kalau begitu,\Naku akan mulai dari awal lagi.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.23,0:13:15.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dahulu kala, di negeri yang jauh,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}hiduplah sepasang kakek dan nenek.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.94,0:13:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kakek pergi ke gunung untuk membabat rumput.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.10,0:13:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Enyah dari sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.02,0:13:21.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.56,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu nenek balapan lari melawan buah persik\Nsampai ke ujung sungai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau pikir kau bisa menyusulku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.58,0:13:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.69,0:13:31.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mereka terdengar seperti\Npasangan lansia yang sangat bugar.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.16,0:13:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Menang!\N- Buah persik adalah hadiah kemenangannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.83,0:13:34.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.28,0:13:36.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Yako.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.31,0:13:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, iya!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.91,0:13:43.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku lupa memberitahumu bahwa Jarashi\Ndan Karma akan segera tiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.98,0:13:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan ruang belakang?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.26,0:13:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggalkan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana dengan barang-barang\Ndi lantai dua?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.70,0:13:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sedang diturunkan sedikit demi sedikit.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.07,0:14:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei! Apa yang kau lakukan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.27,0:14:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, hanya saja tubuhku...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.18,0:14:05.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa masalahnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.50,0:14:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tahu. Tiba-tiba saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.51,0:14:09.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah, ayo berdiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.94,0:14:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa yang harus kita lakukan?\NKirim barang yang sudah dikemas lebih dulu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.30,0:14:14.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, lakukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.50,0:14:15.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oke.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.06,0:14:21.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kikira, apa pelacakannya aman?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.38,0:14:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.24,0:14:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.57,0:14:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi, aku boleh menghajar mereka karena\Nmenculik dan mengurung anak kecil ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.97,0:14:31.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Boleh. Tapi jangan berlebihan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.08,0:14:35.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo cepat selesaikan pekerjaan ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.08,0:14:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, sebelum mobilnya kembali...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.43,0:14:37.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.91,0:14:38.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.55,0:14:47.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.11,0:14:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jika kalian mau bersikap kooperatif,\Naku akan memberi belas kasihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.43,0:14:56.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Mereka menemukan kita!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.02,0:15:03.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Jadi maunya begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.77,0:15:05.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak menginginkan belas kasihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.48,0:15:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.16,0:15:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau tidak apa-apa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.95,0:15:13.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sialan kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.92,0:15:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku minta maaf! Maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.44,0:15:33.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasihanilah aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.32,0:15:37.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyedihkan sekali. Jika mau minta maaf,\Nuntuk apa mencoba melawan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.94,0:15:40.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang untuk ikut dengan tenang.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:41.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Heh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:42.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bodoh! Kau pikir aku akan minta maaf,\NDasar Berotot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.27,0:15:50.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa penggelap uang\Nmembawa pistol segala?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.45,0:15:51.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu kan berbahaya!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.98,0:15:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasakan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.94,0:15:57.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mati kau!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.56,0:16:11.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau harus menambah pekerjaanku lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.43,0:16:14.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seharusnya ini sudah cukup.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.46,0:16:18.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah! Kembali ke sini!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menyerahlah dengan tenang!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.51,0:16:22.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangkap aku kalau bisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.19,0:16:25.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selamat tinggal, Bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak akan kulepaskan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.21,0:16:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berani sekali kau mencoba\Nmelarikan diri dariku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.95,0:16:43.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah kubilang jangan berlebihan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.51,0:16:46.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lampu menyala!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.33,0:16:48.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ketemu!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.18,0:16:51.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak terluka? Kau menangis?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.37,0:16:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak apa-apa.\NAku tidak menangis, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.87,0:16:53.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benarkah?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.93,0:16:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di mana Jarashi?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia sedang menghajar orang-orang jahat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.82,0:16:58.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.63,0:17:02.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.37,0:17:03.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Keren sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.31,0:17:11.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin menangkapnya.\NTolong panggilkan Jarashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.90,0:17:17.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaranya keras sekali!\NApa semuanya baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.82,0:17:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aman. Aku bisa tenang berkat pengalihanmu,\Njadi aku bisa langsung bergerak.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.33,0:17:24.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dongengmu itu menyelamatkan kami.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.42,0:17:27.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa Yu dan yang lainnya juga aman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya. Kami akan segera kembali ke kantor.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.61,0:17:40.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Biji ek berguling-guling...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.79,0:17:45.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gawat, dia jatuh ke dalam...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:46.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.78,0:17:48.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana jalan pulangnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.63,0:18:05.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.16,0:18:07.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.48,0:18:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bulan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.55,0:18:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau baru saja mengatakan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.94,0:18:19.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... Kenapa aku\Nberbaring di pangkuanmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.62,0:18:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau kelelahan setelah semua kejadian tadi,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:25.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}jadi aku yang menyarankannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.94,0:18:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudahlah! Semuanya sudah pulang, kok!\NTidak perlu sungkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.21,0:18:32.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku selalu ingin memelukmu di pangkuanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.51,0:18:34.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Eh...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.24,0:18:36.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin sebentar saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.10,0:18:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berapa lama aku tertidur?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.44,0:18:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sekitar lima belas menit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.31,0:18:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.74,0:18:51.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.04,0:18:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu... tadi ciuman, bukan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.80,0:18:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sangat tiba-tiba...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.02,0:18:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.37,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu... ciuman dewasa\Nseperti yang kubaca di novel roman?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.06,0:19:20.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akira?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.14,0:19:24.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin kau bersamaku selamanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.72,0:19:26.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aki...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.36,0:19:33.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.53,0:19:37.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Tonome!\N- Halo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.65,0:19:38.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.71,0:19:41.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Ada apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.43,0:19:42.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.11,0:19:47.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}- Terima kasih sudah menyelamatkannya.\N- Apa? Kenapa sampai begini?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.14,0:19:48.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, jangan sungkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.30,0:19:50.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Yu! Katakan sesuatu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.63,0:19:51.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.77,0:19:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maafkan aku karena sudah sangat\Nmerepotkanmu hari ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.60,0:19:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, tidak, tidak apa-apa sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.06,0:19:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kami minta maaf karena sudah mengganggu.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalian tidak mengganggu sama sekali, kok!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.89,0:20:03.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hadiahnya kutinggalkan di luar, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.03,0:20:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.62,0:20:10.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}B-Bagaimana kalau kita pulang?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.54,0:20:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.62,0:20:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa kita sudah menjadi\Npelanggan tetap di bar ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.06,0:20:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita kan sudah datang beberapa kali.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.94,0:20:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat pertama kali aku datang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.86,0:20:37.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku melakukan hal-hal memalukan\Nkarena pengaruh alkohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.01,0:20:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Padahal aku belum pernah\Nmenjalin hubungan sebelumnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.32,0:20:42.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menggemaskan sekali saat itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.14,0:20:43.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tolong lupakan kejadian itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.89,0:20:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sama halnya saat pertama kali\Naku mengajakmu berkencan,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.60,0:20:50.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ada satu hal yang kukhawatirkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.48,0:20:51.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.11,0:20:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dilihat dari posisimu,\Naku ini pria yang lebih tua dan atasanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.23,0:20:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku takut jika aku memaksamu pergi\Npadahal kau tidak menginginkannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.36,0:21:01.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja tidak begitu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.28,0:21:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, sekarang aku tahu kalau\Nketakutan itu tidak perlu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, benar sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.62,0:21:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Faktanya, akhir-akhir ini\Naku jadi sangat bergantung padamu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.12,0:21:14.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?! Tidak, aku kan yang memintamu\Nmelakukan sebagian pekerjaan itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.05,0:21:21.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena aku ingin dalam hubungan ini,\Nkita bisa selalu saling mengandalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.72,0:21:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, dan itulah sebabnya...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.42,0:21:24.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.05,0:21:26.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku ingin melakukannya dengan benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.55,0:21:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan benar?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.90,0:21:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukannya aku tidak pernah\Nmemikirkan hal ini sebelumnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.51,0:21:32.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi, Shizuka...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.50,0:21:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maukah kau berpacaran denganku\Nuntuk menuju jenjang pernikahan?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.32,0:21:39.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menikah?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.58,0:21:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa itu jadi masalah?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, anu... Tidak sama sekali!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.60,0:21:45.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}A-Aku ingin menikah! Aku mau!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.96,0:21:46.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kita belum akan menikah sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.95,0:21:48.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Iya, aku tahu!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.75,0:21:52.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu terlalu cepat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.06,0:21:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau menghancurkan suasana tegangnya!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.32,0:22:00.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Habisnya, aku ingin kau terus\Nmenggandeng dan membimbingku.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.96,0:22:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, pertama-tama mungkin kita\Nbisa merencanakan untuk tinggal bersama.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.21,0:22:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tinggal bersama?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.30,0:22:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku siap!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.04,0:22:07.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Belum sekarang.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.96,0:22:09.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mari kita rencanakan bersama-sama.
